Implementation in C++

CThe program is written in C++ and uses:
The string data type to store text.
A for loop to scan each character.
Conditional statements to check character ranges.
ASCII values and modulo operation to manage letter shifting and wrap-around.
This implementation ensures correct results for both uppercase and lowercase letters.


